lead_paragraph: For all of his victories during two decades on the tennis tour, including eight Grand Slam titles, Andre Agassi looks back most fondly these days on the aftermath of a loss.

headline.print_headline: 10 Years After Last Pro Match, Andre Agassi Visits US Open
